03:13.553 --> 03:15.423
Balki your Bibbi Babkas
are so good

03:15.456 --> 03:16.960
I think you could sell them.

03:18.998 --> 03:21.035
Get out of the city.

03:23.006 --> 03:25.611
I wouldn't feel right
taking your money.

03:30.153 --> 03:31.155
No, Balki...

03:31.188 --> 03:32.859
...I don't mean sell them to us

03:32.892 --> 03:34.996
I mean sell them
to other people.

03:35.030 --> 03:36.599
It could be a nice little
business venture.

03:36.633 --> 03:37.736
You could make
a couple of extra bucks

03:37.769 --> 03:40.240
and get a lesson
in free enterprise.

03:40.273 --> 03:41.977
Enterprise?

03:42.010 --> 03:44.014
You mean I could meet
Captain Kirk and Scotty?

03:49.058 --> 03:50.762
[imitates Scotty]
I'll have full power for you
in an hour, captain

03:50.795 --> 03:52.197
but I need more
Dilithium crystals.

03:56.305 --> 03:58.978
No, no, no...

03:59.011 --> 04:00.681
No, Balki.

04:00.714 --> 04:03.019
That's the Starship Enterprise.

04:04.956 --> 04:08.162
Free enterprise is the American
way of doing business.

04:08.196 --> 04:09.632
I tell you what,

04:09.665 --> 04:11.703
you whip up a batch
of Bibbi Babkas

04:11.736 --> 04:13.206
and tomorrow I'll take them
to restaurants

04:13.239 --> 04:14.776
and see if anybody
is interested.

04:14.810 --> 04:18.216
Cousin, Cousin, you don't
just whip up Bibbi Babkas.

04:18.249 --> 04:20.687
I‐I‐I, this took me all morning,

04:20.721 --> 04:23.159
and‐and I'm the best
Bibbi Babka baker on Mypos.

04:24.796 --> 04:28.603
Believe me, baking Bibbi Babkas
is a back‐breaking business.

04:30.206 --> 04:31.676
I understand, Balki.

04:31.709 --> 04:33.680
Baking Bibbi Babkas is
a back‐breaking business

04:33.713 --> 04:34.783
but...

04:37.688 --> 04:39.191
You were doing it alone.

04:39.224 --> 04:41.062
There are four of us.

04:41.095 --> 04:42.330
We'll‐we'll all do it together.

04:42.364 --> 04:43.667
It'll be like a party.

04:43.700 --> 04:45.704
That's a wonderful idea, Larry.

04:45.737 --> 04:47.976
Yeah, what do you say, Balki?

04:48.009 --> 04:51.382
Well, I... I guess we could
bake up a batch of Bibbi Babkas

04:51.415 --> 04:53.052
and see if anybody bites.

04:55.023 --> 04:56.025
Beautiful.

