06:05.030 --> 06:07.735
He wants two thousand.

06:17.020 --> 06:18.823
Let me get this straight.

06:21.128 --> 06:22.999
Today is Saturday.

06:23.032 --> 06:26.205
And this chef wants us to make
2,000 Bibbi Babkas by Monday?

06:26.238 --> 06:27.875
Right.

06:27.909 --> 06:30.881
Larry, it took us all morning
to make three dozen.

06:30.915 --> 06:33.152
