to change lanes.

07:49.605 --> 07:51.676
Well, this is different.

07:51.709 --> 07:54.214
This is the brass ring.
This is the whole enchilada.

07:54.248 --> 07:56.052
The four of us could own
our own company.

07:56.085 --> 07:57.621
Be our own bosses.
What do you say?

07:57.655 --> 07:59.058
Are ya with me?

07:59.091 --> 08:01.128
‐ I'm with you.
‐ I'm with you.

08:01.596 --> 08:03.232
Balki?

08:03.266 --> 08:05.236
No, too much pressure.

08:06.673 --> 08:08.342
