‐ What?

08:11.215 --> 08:16.092
This is your chance
to make Mypos famous.

08:16.125 --> 08:18.763
To put Mypos
on the culinary map.

08:20.233 --> 08:22.738
Well, but, cousin,
baking 2,000 Bibbi Babkas

08:22.771 --> 08:25.076
