What did I just say?

16:31.354 --> 16:32.491
"Ha!"

16:34.962 --> 16:37.468
You got that right.

16:37.501 --> 16:39.136
I'm the only
that knows how to make

16:39.170 --> 16:41.207
Bibbi Babkas with the
special cream filling.

16:41.240 --> 16:42.276
Oh, what's the big deal?

16:42.309 --> 16:45.148
Pinch of this, bit of that,
dollop of whatever.

16:45.984 --> 16:47.186
Oh, is that so?

16:47.219 --> 16:49.356
Well, let me tell you this,
if you don't make‐‐

16:49.392 --> 16:50.527
I tell you what, Balki

16:50.560 --> 16:52.964
if you can't take the heat

16:52.998 --> 16:54.200
get outta my kitchen.

16:57.541 --> 16:58.676
Alright.

17:01.616 --> 17:02.984
Fine.

17:04.353 --> 17:08.663
You've made your cake.
Now, lie in it.

17:18.550 --> 17:20.018
♪ Rup bup bup bup‐pa ♪

17:20.051 --> 17:21.287
♪ Rup bup bup bup‐pa ♪

17:24.292 --> 17:27.066
[instrumental music]

17:32.209 --> 17:35.082
[instrumental music]

17:47.072 --> 17:49.411
[music continues]

17:58.984 --> 18:02.925
Two thousand
Bibbi Babkas, buddy.

18:02.959 --> 18:04.128
You know...

18:04.162 --> 18:07.067
...I think there is a valuable
lesson to be learned here.

18:08.604 --> 18:10.375
You know...

18:10.408 --> 18:12.212
...I think I'm gonna hear it.

18:14.148 --> 18:18.123
Balki, Balki, Balki...

18:18.156 --> 18:21.397
We all want to maintain
the quality of our product.

18:21.430 --> 18:22.565
But you see

18:22.599 --> 18:25.538
to make it in business today,
you've gotta be willing

18:25.571 --> 18:30.114
to sacrifice, persevere,
and yes, compromise a little.

18:34.956 --> 18:35.925
[pops]

18:44.041 --> 18:45.144
What was that?

18:48.216 --> 18:50.588
I think that was one
of your compromises.

18:52.659 --> 18:53.861
[pops]

18:56.199 --> 18:57.469
It's coming from the boxes.

19:06.520 --> 19:09.626
Don't...open...this...box.

19:13.301 --> 19:14.469
What are you talking about?

19:14.503 --> 19:17.642
I'm talking about this box.

19:17.675 --> 19:21.081
And the act of
your not opening it.

19:22.452 --> 19:25.358
Balki, take your
hand off this box.

19:31.637 --> 19:33.474
Alright.

19:33.507 --> 19:36.011
If that what you really want.

19:36.045 --> 19:38.116
That's what I really want. Okay?

19:47.168 --> 19:48.270
[splatters]

20:14.155 --> 20:15.425
The...

20:16.560 --> 20:19.366
The Bibbi Babka... exploded.

20:24.876 --> 20:26.179
In my face.

20:32.392 --> 20:33.427
Well, yes, it did.

20:38.337 --> 20:40.274
And do you know why?

20:42.311 --> 20:45.885
Because if you don't make
the Bibbi Babkas

20:45.918 --> 20:48.857
the traditional Myposian way,

20:48.891 --> 20:52.331
the Bibbi in the Babka
goes boom.

20:58.611 --> 21:01.349
The Bibbi in the Babka
goes boom?

21:04.856 --> 21:06.192
Basically.

21:08.964 --> 21:10.735
[pops]

21:10.768 --> 21:13.707
[popping continues]

21:18.417 --> 21:21.222
[popping continues]

21:40.795 --> 21:43.434
[popping continues]

21:45.505 --> 21:48.210
[instrumental music]

21:56.427 --> 21:58.431
The chef at the hotel
was pretty upset.

22:01.570 --> 22:03.641
You know French is
a colorful language.

22:07.013 --> 22:07.915
I don't speak a word of it

22:07.949 --> 22:10.488
and yet I understood
everything he said.

22:12.825 --> 22:16.399
[sighs]
Balki, I had it all planned.

22:16.433 --> 22:17.569
I know, cousin.

22:17.602 --> 22:18.871
I had a schedule.

22:18.904 --> 22:19.939
Oh, I know, cousin.

22:19.973 --> 22:22.945
‐ I had a customer all lined up.
‐ I‐I know, cousin.

22:22.979 --> 22:26.953
I thought this was how
you started a business.

22:26.987 --> 22:28.390
Could I talk now?

22:28.423 --> 22:29.493
Where did I go wrong?

22:29.526 --> 22:30.695
I guess not.

22:33.834 --> 22:35.538
I'm sorry.

22:35.571 --> 22:37.073
What were you going to say?

22:37.108 --> 22:40.815
Err, there are something's
that just can't be rushed.

22:40.848 --> 22:44.656
Like, antiques, red woods...

22:45.925 --> 22:48.029
...a really good episode
of "Moonlighting."

22:54.943 --> 22:57.482
Any episode of "Moonlighting."

23:00.621 --> 23:01.623
I guess you're right.

23:03.126 --> 23:05.731
You think Jennifer and Mary Anne
will still like me?

23:05.765 --> 23:08.470
Ha, cousin,
of course they will.

23:08.504 --> 23:10.107
Maybe after they rest for a week

23:10.140 --> 23:11.610
and if you send them
some flowers

23:11.643 --> 23:13.446
they might even
speak to you again.

23:15.951 --> 23:18.524
I could send them a few
complimentary Bibbi Babkas.

23:19.859 --> 23:21.429
A few of it didn't explode.

23:28.176 --> 23:29.913
[pops]

23:32.184 --> 23:34.155
‐ Flowers.
‐ Better.

23:34.188 --> 23:37.093
[instrumental music]

23:44.074 --> 23:46.078
